<DIV>Banish Undead: (cleric 44)</DIV>
<DIV>585 damage, 225 mana, 5.5 cast time, 2.25 recast time. neg 50 resist adjust (added later)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Conflagration: (wizard 44)</DIV>
<DIV>606 to 622 damage at 48, 250mana, 5.5 cast time, 2.25 recast time, neg10 resist adjust (in since game started)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>cleric DPS = 75.48, ratio =2.6</DIV>
<DIV>wizard DPS = 78.19 to 80.25, ratio = 2.42 to 2.48</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>however, wizards also got new nukes at 49, that clerics did not get, so wizards really were at </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Rend: (wizard 49)</DIV>
<DIV>774 to 784 at 50, 280mana, 6.3 cast, 2.25 recast, no resist adjust.</DIV>
<DIV>DPS = 91.69 and ratio = 2.8</DIV>
